---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="H2OPE – Lepší spánek, rychlejší regenerace, více energie" hasHero={true}>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/hero-wave-bg-D3SlsVy3.png" alt="" class="hero-wave" />
    </div>
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">AI-Powered Wellness</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        <span class="cs-only">Lepší spánek<br />Rychlejší regenerace<br />Více energie</span>
        <span class="en-only">Better Sleep<br />Faster Recovery<br />More Energy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub"><span class="cs-only">Napsáno životem, podpořeno srdcem.</span><span class="en-only">Written by life, backed by heart.</span></p>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">500+</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label"><span class="cs-only">klientů</span><span class="en-only">clients</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">6 000</span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label"><span class="cs-only">odinhalovaných hodin</span><span class="en-only">inhaled hours</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="hero-stat">
          <span class="hero-stat-num">3 <span class="cs-only">roky</span><span class="en-only">yrs</span></span>
          <span class="hero-stat-label"><span class="cs-only">praxe</span><span class="en-only">of practice</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="/pro-firmy" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Pro firmy →</span><span class="en-only">For Companies →</span></a>
        <a href="/pro-jednotlivce" class="btn btn-outline"><span class="cs-only">Pro jednotlivce</span><span class="en-only">For Individuals</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CO JE MOLEKULÁRNÍ VODÍK -->
  <section class="molecule-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mol-header">
        <h2 class="mol-title"><span class="cs-only">Co je molekulární vodík?</span><span class="en-only">What is Molecular Hydrogen?</span></h2>
        <p class="mol-sub"><span class="cs-only">Jednoduše vysvětleno, bez zbytečného žargonu</span><span class="en-only">Simply explained, without unnecessary jargon</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="mol-grid">
        <div class="mol-card">
          <div class="mol-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
              <path d="M12 2a10 4.5 0 0 1 0 9"/>
              <path d="M12 2a10 4.5 0 0 0 0 9"/>
              <ellipse cx="12" cy="12" rx="10" ry="4.5"/>
              <path d="M12 15a10 4.5 0 0 1 0 7"/>
              <path d="M12 15a10 4.5 0 0 0 0 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Co to je</span><span class="en-only">What It Is</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Molekulární vodík (H₂) je nejmenší molekula ve vesmíru. Díky své velikosti se může dostat prakticky kamkoli v těle – tam, kam větší molekuly nemají přístup.</span><span class="en-only">Molecular hydrogen (H₂) is the smallest molecule in the universe. Due to its size, it can reach practically anywhere in the body.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="mol-card">
          <div class="mol-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Proč se používá</span><span class="en-only">Why It's Used</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Lidé vodík využívají pro podporu regenerace, energie a celkové pohody. Není to lék, ale podpůrný wellness nástroj pro ty, kdo chtějí o sebe pečovat aktivněji.</span><span class="en-only">People use hydrogen to support recovery, energy, and overall wellbeing. It's not a medicine, but a supportive wellness tool.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="mol-card">
          <div class="mol-icon">
            <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1" ry="1"/>
              <path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"/>
              <path d="M9 12h6M9 16h4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Jak terapie probíhá</span><span class="en-only">How Therapy Works</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Konzultace → personalizovaný plán → pravidelné inhalace → průběžné sledování a úpravy programu dle Vašich potřeb.</span><span class="en-only">Consultation → personalized plan → regular inhalations → ongoing monitoring and adjustments based on your needs.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="mol-card mol-cta-card">
          <p class="mol-cta-label"><span class="cs-only">Zajímá vás více?</span><span class="en-only">Want to know more?</span></p>
          <a href="/jak-to-funguje" class="btn btn-orange"><span class="cs-only">Chci vědět více →</span><span class="en-only">Learn More →</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mol-disclaimer">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0;color:var(--cyan)">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
        </svg>
        <span><span class="cs-only">H2OPE neposkytuje lékařské služby. Vodíková terapie je wellness program a nenahrazuje odbornou lékařskou péči.</span><span class="en-only">H2OPE does not provide medical services. Hydrogen therapy is a wellness program and does not replace professional medical care.</span></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROČ NA KANCLU -->
  <section class="office-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="office-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Pro firmy</span><span class="en-only">For Companies</span></p>
          <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Proč mít vodík na kanclu?</span><span class="en-only">Why Have Hydrogen at the Office?</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Protože je to skvělý benefit pro zaměstnance, ale pozor ještě lepší pro zaměstnavatele 🙂</span><span class="en-only">Because it's a great benefit for employees, but watch out – it's even better for employers 🙂</span></p>
          <ul class="office-list">
            <li>
              <span class="office-check">✓</span>
              <span><span class="cs-only">Zaměstnanci mají lepší koncentraci a efektivitu</span><span class="en-only">Employees have better concentration and efficiency</span></span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="office-check">✓</span>
              <span><span class="cs-only">Sníží se nemocnost ve firmě</span><span class="en-only">Reduced illness in the company</span></span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="office-check">✓</span>
              <span><span class="cs-only">Lidé mají více energie</span><span class="en-only">People have more energy</span></span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-orange" data-open-modal="contact" style="margin-top:2rem;display:inline-flex"><span class="cs-only">Chci nezávaznou konzultaci a zjistit více</span><span class="en-only">I want a free consultation and more info</span></button>
        </div>
        <div class="office-visual">
          <img src="/images/audience-corporate-Dn4o_vV9.jpg" alt="Firemní wellness" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VIDEO -->
  <section class="video-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="video-wrap">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AHFvYkVjhus"
          title="H2OPE Hydrogen Therapy"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JAK FUNGUJE - 6 KROKŮ -->
  <section class="steps-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Jak funguje vodíková terapie u H2OPE</span><span class="en-only">How Hydrogen Therapy Works at H2OPE</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">6 jednoduchých kroků k lepšímu zdraví</span><span class="en-only">6 simple steps to better health</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">01</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Workshop a nastavení</span><span class="en-only">Workshop & Setup</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Přijedeme za vámi, vše vám ukážeme a společně nastavíme.</span><span class="en-only">We'll come to you, show you everything, and set it up together.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">02</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Rychlý dotazník</span><span class="en-only">Quick Questionnaire</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Pár otázek pro správné doporučení na míru.</span><span class="en-only">A few questions for the right personalized recommendation.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">03</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Vyhodnocení</span><span class="en-only">Assessment</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">H2OPE Score a klíčové oblasti zaměření.</span><span class="en-only">H2OPE Score and key areas of focus.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">04</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Individuální plán</span><span class="en-only">Individual Plan</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Plán pro každého zaměstnance (volitelně testy pro větší přesnost).</span><span class="en-only">A plan for each employee (optional tests for greater accuracy).</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">05</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Inhalace v kanceláři</span><span class="en-only">Office Inhalation</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Jednoduchá sezení podle plánu.</span><span class="en-only">Simple sessions according to plan.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">06</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Průběžná péče</span><span class="en-only">Ongoing Care</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Úpravy podle dat a zpětné vazby.</span><span class="en-only">Adjustments based on data and feedback.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-top:3rem">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-orange" data-open-modal="contact"><span class="cs-only">Chci nezávaznou konzultaci</span><span class="en-only">I want a free consultation</span></button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRO KOHO - CAROUSEL -->
  <section class="audience-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Pro koho je vodíková terapie</span><span class="en-only">Who Is Hydrogen Therapy For</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Každý má jiné cíle. Vyberte oblast, která je vám nejbližší.</span><span class="en-only">Everyone has different goals. Select the area closest to you.</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="aud-filters">
        <p class="aud-filters-label"><span class="cs-only">Poznáte se v tom?</span><span class="en-only">Can you relate?</span></p>
        <div class="aud-tabs-row">
          <button class="aud-tab active" data-goto="0" data-category="work">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v2M8 7V5a2 2 0 0 1 4 0"/></svg>
            <span class="cs-only">H₂EKTICKÁ PRÁCE?</span><span class="en-only">H₂ECTIC WORK?</span>
          </button>
          <button class="aud-tab" data-goto="3" data-category="home">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
            <span class="cs-only">H₂URIKÁN DOMA?</span><span class="en-only">H₂URRICANE AT HOME?</span>
          </button>
          <button class="aud-tab" data-goto="4" data-category="sports">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
            <span class="cs-only">H₂ROZNÉ POČASÍ?</span><span class="en-only">H₂ARIABLE WEATHER?</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <p class="aud-hashtag">#frcimenavodiku</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="aud-carousel-wrap">
      <button class="aud-nav aud-nav-prev" id="audPrev" aria-label="Předchozí">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
      </button>

      <div class="aud-stage" id="audStage">
        <div class="aud-card" data-index="0" data-category="work">
          <img src="/images/audience-corporate-Dn4o_vV9.jpg" alt="Korporátní klienti" />
          <div class="aud-overlay">
            <div class="aud-card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v2M8 7V5a2 2 0 0 1 4 0"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="aud-card-content">
              <h3><span class="cs-only">Korporátní klienti</span><span class="en-only">Corporate Clients</span></h3>
              <span class="aud-tag"><span class="cs-only">H₂EKTICKÁ PRÁCE?</span><span class="en-only">H₂ECTIC WORK?</span></span>
              <p><span class="cs-only">Wellness benefit pro zaměstnance. Podpora regenerace a energie během náročného pracovního období. Možnost on-site terapeutických dnů.</span><span class="en-only">Wellness benefit for employees. Supporting recovery and energy during demanding work periods.</span></p>
              <a href="/pro-firmy" class="aud-link"><span class="cs-only">Řešení pro firmy →</span><span class="en-only">Business Solutions →</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="aud-card" data-index="1" data-category="other">
          <img src="/images/audience-oncology-CSZjQL9Q.jpg" alt="Onkologičtí pacienti" />
          <div class="aud-overlay">
            <div class="aud-card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="aud-card-content">
              <h3><span class="cs-only">Onkologičtí pacienti</span><span class="en-only">Oncology Patients</span></h3>
              <span class="aud-tag"><span class="cs-only">PODPŮRNÁ PÉČE</span><span class="en-only">SUPPORTIVE CARE</span></span>
              <p><span class="cs-only">Podpůrná péče zaměřená na komfort, regeneraci a rovnováhu. Citlivý přístup pro období zvýšené zátěže.</span><span class="en-only">Supportive care focused on comfort, recovery, and balance. A sensitive approach for periods of increased stress.</span></p>
              <a href="#kontakt" class="aud-link"><span class="cs-only">Individuální konzultace →</span><span class="en-only">Individual Consultation →</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="aud-card" data-index="2" data-category="other">
          <img src="/images/audience-autoimmune-D8k6ORg3.jpg" alt="Autoimunitní onemocnění" />
          <div class="aud-overlay">
            <div class="aud-card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="aud-card-content">
              <h3><span class="cs-only">Autoimunitní onemocnění</span><span class="en-only">Autoimmune Conditions</span></h3>
              <span class="aud-tag"><span class="cs-only">DLOUHODOBÁ PÉČE</span><span class="en-only">LONG-TERM CARE</span></span>
              <p><span class="cs-only">Podpora celkové rovnováhy a regenerace při dlouhodobých zdravotních výzvách. Jemný a zodpovědný přístup.</span><span class="en-only">Supporting overall balance and recovery in long-term health challenges.</span></p>
              <a href="#kontakt" class="aud-link"><span class="cs-only">Zjistit možnosti →</span><span class="en-only">Explore Options →</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="aud-card" data-index="3" data-category="home">
          <img src="/images/audience-family-DSpp3RU4.jpg" alt="Děti a rodina" />
          <div class="aud-overlay">
            <div class="aud-card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="aud-card-content">
              <h3><span class="cs-only">Děti a rodina</span><span class="en-only">Children & Family</span></h3>
              <span class="aud-tag"><span class="cs-only">H₂URIKÁN DOMA?</span><span class="en-only">H₂URRICANE AT HOME?</span></span>
              <p><span class="cs-only">Jemný přístup pro celou rodinu. Děti pouze v doprovodu rodičů. Bezpečnost a zodpovědnost na prvním místě.</span><span class="en-only">A gentle approach for the whole family. Children only with parental supervision.</span></p>
              <a href="#kontakt" class="aud-link"><span class="cs-only">Konzultace pro rodiče →</span><span class="en-only">Parent Consultation →</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="aud-card" data-index="4" data-category="sports">
          <img src="/images/audience-sports-DLvN4tBA.jpg" alt="Sportovci" />
          <div class="aud-overlay">
            <div class="aud-card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="aud-card-content">
              <h3><span class="cs-only">Sportovci</span><span class="en-only">Athletes</span></h3>
              <span class="aud-tag"><span class="cs-only">H₂ROZNÉ POČASÍ?</span><span class="en-only">H₂ARIABLE WEATHER?</span></span>
              <p><span class="cs-only">Podpora regenerace, výkonnosti a tréninkové rovnováhy. Rychlejší zotavení před i po zátěži.</span><span class="en-only">Supporting recovery, performance, and training balance.</span></p>
              <a href="#kontakt" class="aud-link"><span class="cs-only">Pro sportovce →</span><span class="en-only">For Athletes →</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button class="aud-nav aud-nav-next" id="audNext" aria-label="Další">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="aud-dots" id="audDots">
      <button class="aud-dot active" data-index="0"></button>
      <button class="aud-dot" data-index="1"></button>
      <button class="aud-dot" data-index="2"></button>
      <button class="aud-dot" data-index="3"></button>
      <button class="aud-dot" data-index="4"></button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROČ H2OPE -->
  <section class="why-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Proč H2OPE</span><span class="en-only">Why H2OPE</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Co nás odlišuje od ostatních</span><span class="en-only">What sets us apart</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">👤</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Individuální přístup</span><span class="en-only">Individual Approach</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Každý plán je přizpůsobený vašim cílům, zdravotnímu stavu a životnímu stylu.</span><span class="en-only">Each plan is tailored to your goals, health status, and lifestyle.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">📊</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Strukturovaný proces</span><span class="en-only">Structured Process</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Od prvního dotazníku po průběžné úpravy – vše je jasné, měřitelné a transparentní.</span><span class="en-only">From the first questionnaire to ongoing adjustments – everything is clear, measurable, and transparent.</span></p>
        </div>
